<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.4.8">
<l>piccac ciṟupī lipiṭit tulakil piṇantiṉ maṭavā ravarpō laṅṅaṉē</l>
<l>yacca milarnā ṇilarā taṉmaiyā lavarcey kaiveṟut taṇimā malarttūy</l>
<l>nacci namaṉā raṭaiyā mainamak karuḷce yeṉavuḷ kuḻaintār vamoṭu</l>
<l>niccam niṉaivārk karuḷcey yumavaṟ kiṭammā malaiyā vatunīr malaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place for him who gives grace to those who</l>
<l rend="indent">always meditate with love, [their] hearts melting,</l>
<l>As [they] say, “Give us grace so that [we] do not reach Yama,”</l>
<l rend="indent">devotedly with large, beautiful, pure flowers,</l>
<l>Distaining the actions [done] through idiocy of those in the world</l>
<l rend="indent">clutching little peacock feather [fans], who are without fear [of scorn],</l>
<l>[And] without shame like corpse-eating [demon] women,</l>
<l rend="indent">is the great mountain, namely Nīrmalai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
